{"title":"【070】CSS边框","slug":"hell0-world18","date":"2022-10-04T03:22:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:17:52.408Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world18.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                border                     border-style","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>border</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./border-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1></h1>\n    <p class=\"a\"> \n        border-style<span id=\"more\"></span>:dotted/dashed/solid/double/none/hidden<br><br>\n        border-width:px/em/thin,medium,thick<br><br>\n        border-color:\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"b\">\n        写table>(tr>td*3)*3 tab键\n    </p>\n    <table border=\"1\">\n        <tr>\n            <td>左上</td>\n            <td>中上</td>\n            <td>右上</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"a\">左中</td>\n            <td class=\"b\">中</td>\n            <td>右中</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>左下</td>\n            <td>中下</td>\n            <td>右下</td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>   \n    <p class=\"c\">\n        当表格单元格相邻边框产生冲突时,border-style: hidden>solid>...none优先级高到低。<br><br>\n        控制表格中单独的一根线,可在border-style中间添加一个表示方向的词,如border-top-style就可设置单个边框线。可设置top,right,bottom,left方向。除了单个属性外，border-style属性值可使用混合的简写方法<br><br>\n        1:四个值如dotted solid double dashed;(上，右，下，左)<br><br>\n        2:三个值如dotted solid double;(上，左右，下)<br><br>\n        3:两个值如dotted solid:（上下，左右）<br><br>\n        4:四个值如dotted(四边)<br><br>\n    </p><br><br>  \n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}